{"type":"message","id":"b171c0af","parentId":"d95ae252","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:31:25.632Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ef06e089f63a4676a4ca46ba","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"* 1720174 (HEAD -> main, origin/main, origin/HEAD) fix: auto-close no-ci PR label and document triage labels\n* 5decb00 fix(swiftformat): sync GatewayModels exclusions with OpenClawProtocol (#41242)\n* 6b87489 Revert \"feat(ui): add chat infrastructure modules (slice 1 of dashboard-v2)\"\n* 9f0a64f Revert \"Update ui/src/ui/chat/export.ts\"\n* 8e412ba Revert \"fix(ui): address review feedback on chat infra slice\"\n* 8a6cd80 fix(ui): address review feedback on chat infra slice\n* d648dd7 Update ui/src/ui/chat/export.ts\n* 5a659b0 feat(ui): add chat infrastructure modules (slice 1 of dashboard-v2)\n* c0cba7f Fix one-shot exit hangs by tearing down cached memory managers (#40389)\n* b48291e Exec: mark child command env with OPENCLAW_CLI (#41411)\n* 4790e40 fix(plugins): expose model auth API to context-engine plugins (#41090)\n* c9a6c54 Add HTTP 499 to transient error codes for model fallback (#41468)\n* de4c3db Logging: harden probe suppression for observations (#41338)\n* 64746c1 fix(discord): apply effective maxLinesPerMessage in live replies (#40133)\n* 56f787e build(protocol): regenerate Swift models after pending node work schemas (#41477)\n* 531e836 Agents: add fallback error observations (#41337)\n* 3c34743 acp: harden follow-up reliability and attachments (#41464)\n* 0669b0d fix(agents): probe single-provider billing cooldowns (#41422)\n* 0c7f078 acp: add regression coverage and smoke-test docs (#41456)\n* 4aebff7 acp: forward attachments into ACP runtime sessions (#41427)\n* 8e3f3bc acp: enrich streaming updates for ide clients (#41442)\n* 30340d6 Sandbox: import STATE_DIR from paths directly (#41439)\n* d346f2d acp: restore session context and controls (#41425)\n* e6e4169 acp: fail honestly in bridge mode (#41424)\n* 1bc59cc Gateway: tigh